@host = http://localhost:8080

### Fetch all issues (no filters)
GET {{host}}/api/issues

### Fetch issues with pagination
GET {{host}}/api/issues?page=1&per_page=20

### Fetch open issues
GET {{host}}/api/issues?state=opened

### Fetch closed issues
GET {{host}}/api/issues?state=closed

### Fetch issues by assignee
GET {{host}}/api/issues?assignee_id=123

### Fetch issues by author
GET {{host}}/api/issues?author_id=456

### Fetch issues with specific labels
GET {{host}}/api/issues?labels=bug,critical

### Search issues
GET {{host}}/api/issues?search=performance

### Fetch issues for a milestone
GET {{host}}/api/issues?milestone=v1.0

### Complex query with multiple filters
GET {{host}}/api/issues?state=opened&assignee_id=123&labels=bug&order_by=created_at&sort=desc&page=1&per_page=50
